  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
        <div rend="parallel">
            <lg xml:id="TK889">
<l>eṭpaka vaṉṉa ciṟumaittē yāyiṉu</l>
<l>muṭpakai yuḷḷatāṅ kēṭu</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Although internal hatred be as small as the fragment of the sesamum (seed), still does destruction dwell in it.</l>
            </lg>
        </div>
    </body>
